room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by The Greatest Escape Games in Colorado Springs
room_address: 801 South Tejon Street Colorado Springs, CO 80903
room_description: You and your friends are partners with Sourdough Joe in a gold mine. He dies before he has a chance to tell you the location of the mine and registering the claim at the Assay Office. You must find the map in his cabin and register it before closing time today or you lose your rights to the claim as partners.
